# &quot;Nothoscordum moconense&quot; - Misiones in Argentina
# &quot;Nothoscordum modestum&quot; - Paraguay
# &quot;Nothoscordum montevidense&quot; - Uruguay, northern Argentina, southern Brazil
# &quot;Nothoscordum muscorum&quot; – Rio Grande do Sul in southern Brazil
