# &quot;Nothoscordum vernum&quot; - central Chile
# &quot;Nothoscordum vigilense&quot; - Jujuy in Argentina
# &quot;Nothoscordum vittatum&quot; - Uruguay, northern Argentina, southern Brazil
# &quot;Nothoscordum yalaense&quot; - Jujuy in Argentina
# &quot;Nothoscordum yatainum&quot; - Corrientes in Argentina
===Formerly included===
Several species formerly placed in &quot;Nothoscordum&quot; are now accepted in other genera, including &quot;Allium, Latace, Oziroe, and Tristagma.&quot; We provide links to help you find appropriate information.
